    "description": "踏上一场穿越无尽、不断变化的小镇的惊悚之旅，在这款3D心理游戏中，你需要找到通往 42号州际公路的唯一出路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.poster.avif?t=1732998224\" width=590 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.webm?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/42d564f7a911be13dd8f92a5ed006776.mp4?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在你驾驶的过程中，细微的环境变化会不断挑战你的感知力和注意力。一旦发现异常，立即右转一—正确的选择将带<br>你一步步接近出口。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.poster.avif?t=1732998224\" width=590 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.webm?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191630/extras/ea1b7da80cd7ad2b0e75447ce5db6489.mp4?t=1732998224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但请小心-若你忽视了异常你将被幻觉引入歧途，被困于无尽的循环之中。你能在这场扭曲的现实中保持多久的理智？",
